## Core Features

### Mandatory job selection
Workers must select a job to clock in.  
Every hour is tied to a revenue event.

### Magic link worker access
SMS-based magic link.  
No passwords.  
No apps to install.  
Clock-in in under 10 seconds.

### Job labour summary
See labour hours and cost per job.  
This is the core retention screen.

Owners don’t buy time tracking.  
They buy visibility into profit.

### Payroll export
CSV with job attribution and labour cost.  
QuickBooks-friendly.  
No more spreadsheet gymnastics.

### Weekly labour email
Every week you receive:

“Last week’s labour cost by job.”

Margin awareness becomes habit.

### Payroll leak detection
Automatic flags for:

- Overlapping shifts  
- Excessively long shifts  
- Missing clock-outs  

Catch leakage before payday.

